<div style="color: #ff2baa; font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; text-align: center; padding: 2px 10px;">
<p><tt>Deep beneath the ocean of ideas and consciousness, a magenta form still swims, jubilantly laughing as she dives and twirls through schools of the mesmerizing, brightly-lit creatures of the dark sea.</tt><br />
<tt>She cannot help but reach out to touch every single one.</tt></p>
